cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.RO, cs.SE 

The paper proposes a novel model-free multi-objective reinforcement learning approach for adaptive optimal control of manufacturing processes. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The approach is applied to control manufacturing processes, which suggests that the paper is also likely to belong to the Systems and Control (cs.SY) and Robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories. Finally, the paper proposes an approach for adaptive optimal control, which suggests that it may also belong to the Software Engineering (cs.SE) sub-category.
